<p>
  From coordinating the logistics of remote production to shaping the doc’s
  narrative structure and guiding interview subjects, I ensured the story was
  compelling, authentic, and engaging for BoomTV’s audience of gamers and fans.
  My focus was on creating a piece that highlights Riley’s trajectory from
  unknown talent to top-earner, while resonating with fans by showcasing the
  personal growth and challenges of a modern esports competitor.
</p>

<img
  src="/assets/img/projects/next-level/vlcsnap-2025-05-10-20h36m32s754.jpg"
