<p>
  I worked closely with Riley and his family to source archive images, map out
  his day-to-day life, and conduct introspective pre-interviews that helped
  inform the project and its emotional tone. Directing the film remotely, I
  oversaw on-location shoots and interviews timed with a major esports
  tournament. The result: an immersive, honest portrait of a modern competitor
  under pressure, told through the lens of the challenges that shaped him.
</p>

